(3456, 4, '2015-03-01 23:49:31', '2015-03-02 04:49:31', '[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1468238808291{padding-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_images_carousel images=\"3460,3457,3458,3459\" img_size=\"full\" speed=\"3000\" slides_per_view=\"2\" autoplay=\"yes\" hide_pagination_control=\"yes\" hide_prev_next_buttons=\"yes\" wrap=\"yes\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<a href=\"www.lizlovely.com\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-3462 size-full\" src=\"http://flexiblecapitalfund.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Encore-Renewable-Energy-Logo.png\" width=\"265\" height=\"80\" /></a>Encore Renewable Energy is an integrated clean energy company focused on commercial, industrial and community-scale solar PV systems and solutions for underutilized property such as landfills, brownfields and rooftops. As of 2015, Encore has delivered 37 projects along the Eastern seaboard, totaling over 12 megawatts of renewable energy since they were founded in 2007. Encore has demonstrated leadership in the commercial and community-scale solar industry, helping drive the region towards a more sustainable, clean energy economy.\r\n\r\nA recent <a href=\"https://www.bcorporation.net/\" target=\"_blank\">Certified B Corporation</a>®, Encore has deep commitment to the mission of doing business better—a central tenet of being a Flex Fund portfolio company. As a B Corporation, Encore is among more than 1,700 leading businesses that have met rigorous standards of social and environmental performance, accountability, and transparency.\r\n\r\nThe Flex Fund provided Encore permanent working capital in the form of royalty financing to enable Encore to hire new staff for business development, engineering, and project management at a critical growth juncture.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1468189093639{padding-top: 30px !important;padding-bottom: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column][qbox title1=\"Chad Farrell, President\"]\r\n<h4><em>\"We are thrilled to be able to count the Flexible Capital Fund as an investor in Encore as they are exactly the type of capital partner we are looking to work with given their commitment to the clean energy economy, environmental issues, and the creation of high quality jobs in our home state of Vermont. The Flex Fund is a mission-driven lender that invests in growing Vermont companies who are on the forefront of building new markets that contribute to the current and future environmental, social, and economic health of Vermont and the region.\"</em></h4>\r\n[/qbox][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Encore Renewable Energy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'encore-renewable-energy', '', '', '2016-09-07 16:23:12', '2016-09-07 20:23:12', '', 0, 'http://flexiblecapitalfund.com/?post_type=creativo_portfolio&#038;p=3456', 0, 'creativo_portfolio', '', 0),
